hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: How much were you paid in your last job? breastfast.pl There was also a line about “how long this thing is going to stay up”. Then, after a couple of jokes about what the sculpture might symbolise (“the peril of genetically modified food”, or “French sporting pride brought from Paris to London” after a second successive triumph at the Tour de France by an Englishman), he concluded by returning to his main theme. “Ladies and gentlemen! Here it is! The big blue…” Go on, Boris, just say it. “…Bird!”
